Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:09.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:54.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:59.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:14.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:21.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:28.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have lived all this time\Nwithout ever making a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I failed to become an eternal maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I failed to make my way to\Nthat other world. I remained here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:53.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to touch another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:58.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to feel another's\Nembrace. And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:01.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did they do that to your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I refused to\Nchoose a permanent gender...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they sentenced me to become\Nthe gatekeeper of the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:13.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you wouldn't choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:18.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that no future maiden\Nwould make the same mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,To stand here for all time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:24.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is my penance for\Nrunning away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:45.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Choices
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:51.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is to be\Nofficially disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:54.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, we have decided that it is\Nnow time for you to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:54.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:56.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are we also being stripped\Nof our posts as sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,You will be ceding your duties\Nto the Plumbum priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:04.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:11.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,They won't even let us be Simoun\Nsibyllae anymore? Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll have to leave the Arcus Prima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:21.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, forcing them to make a\Ndecision like that so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can hardly expect them to\Nchoose on such short notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They need time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,They need time to prepare.\NWe are out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:28.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we're asking for is a short period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:32.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Compared to the long history\Nof Simulacrum Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it would only be a fleeting moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,You heard what's happening to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be leaving\Nthe Arcus Prima as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kyuukoku won't be flying\Nthe Simouns any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,And to prove it, the entire maintenance\Ncrew is being moved to the highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's all the same to us\Nno matter where we end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are the\Ndivine vessels of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how close I try to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:21.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, the truth is that I've\Ndiscovered something about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer care about the Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,As long as I know you're safe,\Nthat's enough to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and despise me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're getting smaller, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:51.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become a man and putter\Naround with you and the Simouns, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which are you going to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you've always\Nwanted to become a man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You probably couldn't care less that\Nwe're being forced to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. You've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's so not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm scared too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It scares me that we\Nhave to grow up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to lean on someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want someone to protect me! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up, you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a dummy you are, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:52.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy... dummy... dummy... dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:06:00.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Picking a fight with your sister?\NI mean, how immature is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still just kids. You're\Nboth too young to become adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:12.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Vura, all the Chor Rubor girls\Nalready picked their genders, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ones who had a family\Nbusiness to take over became male.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,The others, well, it was pretty random.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:24.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? Whatever. I don't really\Ncare which I end up being!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, if I were in love, I would\Nbe telling a different story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:31.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really? But everyone says that\Nyou've got a thing for Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, and I've told them over\Nand over that it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, for heaven's sake.\NWhat does it matter, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:39.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,For some reason I feel so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what growing up is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,So if you feel lonely,\Nit means you've grown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alty was such a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Darn it, didn't I tell\Nyou not to tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're always slowing me down, Alty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you're such a dummy, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a dummy?\NYou clumsy slowpoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whatever! You can find your\Nown way back then, you wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're such a dummy, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if we were in the\Nmiddle of a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she could never come up\Nwith any names to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,She could never say\Nanything except, "Dummy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the thing is she never learned.\NShe just kept following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean, really... What a\Nlittle moron of a sister I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:00.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder when it was\Nthat Alty stopped being...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...such a little wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to protect you, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:10.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,She got such an assertive look\Nin her eyes, and she grew so tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was like she suddenly became\Nmore of a grownup than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But because so much was\Ngoing on, I didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:23.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,To me, Alty was still\Nthe same little wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I've always averted my gaze from\Nher. I just didn't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so... I...\NYou'll be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if you're no longer a sibylla, that\Ndoesn't mean you can't do certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like forgiving one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,To forgive someone for wronging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and to be forgiven in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can manage to do that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:50.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I think we can still call ourselves\Nsibyllae even after we choose our gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really do like you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,My feelings for you won't change\Nwhether I become a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever\Nstop looking up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say that the high priestess\Nhas been driven from the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, we don't have much time. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind, don't answer\Nthat. I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,You just want to see Amuria again. That's\Nwhy you want to go to the other world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't do a Ri Majon with you\Nif that's all you care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did Onasia show that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to feel another's embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:10:00.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia... Is she doomed\Nto stand there forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to know forgiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never to be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:14.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that I should take\Nsome of Mamina's things with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh. Her trunk is under her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I go home, I'll be\Nseeing Mamina's mother, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I could give them to her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still smells like Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I hope Mamina's mother\Nwill find comfort in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:40.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder... Is it even possible\Nfor us to save anybody now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can barely take care\Nof ourselves as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if we try our utmost,\Nthen maybe we can save...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,...at least one person in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,One person...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, is there someone in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,That one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:12.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. I hear the highland soldiers\Nare looking for her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe she decided she\Ndidn't want to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, not Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:23.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,She must have realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever! Being\Nsuch a stranger to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,She just got up and left\Nwithout saying a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:34.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but once Chor Tempest is disbanded,\Nwe'll all be going our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:42.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have something to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,About another world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way! Who knew the Emerald Ri\NMajon could do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, but that's precisely\Nwhat's going to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Each of us is going to\Nchoose a gender soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,And our days on the Arcus\NPrima will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those two won't be choosing a\Ngender and will stay the way they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not choose a gender...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and stay the way they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,When the rest of us are all grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the emotions we carry\Ninside us now have faded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two will be\Nalive in another era...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:51.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...somewhere in a sparkling world,\Nlooking just as they do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it. So those two will always...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it. So those two will always...\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even after we've all become adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:05.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they'll stay the same\Nfor us for all time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,The "eternal present"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:14.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go to the other\Nworld with me if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:18.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,But whatever it is we decide,\Nwe really should tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,That we're not going to the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do want to know what\Nhappened to Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do want to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't lie to you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one I'm in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:51.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one who lives facing life, rather\Nthan death... It's you whom I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:56.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one who rescued me from the\Ndarkness... It's you whom I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thought of going to that\Nother world frightens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if you and I are\Ntogether, then I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:09.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that I wanted you to tell\Nme all about your feelings for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't need to give me an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just thought that\NI should let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to let you know. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to take\Nthat in all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one I'm in love with... is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:37.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,To save the drifting spirits\Nof my fallen comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the one thing I've\Nalways had on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But deep down, I always knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:47.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it's not possible\Nto save the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:49.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's one who even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:58.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I realized was that there's one\Nperson who can only be saved by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I'd hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:11.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to hear those very words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:17.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never chose a gender for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was not able to hold\Non to my maiden's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:27.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now, once again,\NI am trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,This time burdening you with\Nall my responsibilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can hear quite a commotion out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That voice... it must be Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, were you planning\Nto stay in bed all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's our last day on the Arcus Prima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Alty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing view!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:36.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, dance with me, Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:30.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, let the Messis\Ntransport you to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:31.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:36.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride\Non a helical-motor train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,May I ask what's going on with\NSibylla Neviril and Sibylla Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,They have asked for a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll come back to say\Nhello when we're adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:39.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,The mountains are getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:49.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had them pack us something to eat\Nbefore we left. Is anybody hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:53.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like a vegetable sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you, Roatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,A meat sandwich for me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Same for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:07.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is for Roatre.\NThis one's yours, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:07.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\NMan, why didn't you tell us sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that you had sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:24.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:48.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:52.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:59.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:07.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:19.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:24.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:33.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:38.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:44.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:47.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:53.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:59.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:05.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:09.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The girls embark on their\Njourney towards adulthood...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.17,0:24:12.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as Neviril and Aer head\Ntowards the "eternal present."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.44,0:24:15.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:16.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:17.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair\NPair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:20.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair
